title: Lana Del Rey (500 Songs) July 2013

Please note: Not all songs may be in the highest quality available online for download or purchase, this is just what I have and I would appreciate if you didn't complain about the quality. 

Includes: All official albums, remixes, demos & unreleased songs by Lana Del Rey as of July 31st 2013. Anything that comes out or leaks after that date will not be included. Songs I am missing will be listed at the end of the list.
